{"tid":2082160,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"International City of Hong Kong 海外建港","createTime":"2020-06-27T19:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T12:17:05.000Z","uid":115579,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"47b4ed435dc3028997db9e5932585b01ce0a93ff","tid":2082160,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T19:59:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bziAhRY4eXE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbziAhRY4eXE&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtGAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=3749ebed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bziAhRY4eXE</a><br />\n<br />\nSaying establish a new city for Hong Kong citizen. As there are many demand of immigration,  it is a good try to develop a new special city for those demand. <br />\n<br />\nRather than copy the Hong Kong, <br />\nIvan said it is just a immigration  and city development plan,  for those people can live together,  sharing the same value and culture. <br />\nHong Kong people are really hard working . <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> we go to work by bus. <br />\n<br />\nd英文真心唔撚掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先正視聽，share唔代表我贊同佢講<br />\n只係覺得，總有一部分人係有錢有能力，一部分係冇錢有能力，既然真係頂唔順支共香港，要走不如有個plan咁走，保存香港嘅文化。<br />\n<br />\n如果只係純粹移民，你好快就冇左你本身嘅身份認同，移民左去台灣嘅港人下一代仲會覺得自己係香港人？最好一定係有個島俾你建港，但未做到嘅話寄人籬下都可能要。"},{"pid":"b7a1eb60ecd7e58452935b5c0f34a7b3dd889d93","tid":2082160,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T20:03:57.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人諗過買哂成個澎湖黎發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a158adf6f77052e5e75ab5e60b6cb16a003483","tid":2082160,"uid":3873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:37:34.000Z","msg":"呢個International Charter City方案真係可以考慮下，可以俾人走難之餘又可以作為一個新城市去試唔同嘅政策同apply新科技，不過真係要避免變成下一個唐人街"},{"pid":"613fc516d9507b8eca23c8a1dcc112b2887e1388","tid":2082160,"uid":361247